name: Satoshi's Cyphers 01
description: The Key text to solve all 12 of these cyphers will be available on the mainpage of satoshiscrypt.com at 11:59 PM PST 4/18/2021. The first to solve each of these cyphers will receive an Archetype Tarot 1 of 1 NFT Trophy on Tezos from Salvador Satoshi. Best of luck to you all. X=Paragraph, Y=Word, Z=Letter 1-2-2  2-4-4  4-9-3  5-9-1  4-5-1  3-2-3  4-5-8  5-9-1  2-4-4
